        <Summary xml:lang="en">An open source tool to create bootable USB drives for ISO/WIM/IMG/VHD(x)/EFI files</Summary>
        <Description xml:lang="en">Ventoy is an open source tool to create bootable USB drive for ISO/WIM/IMG/VHD(x)/EFI files. With Ventoy, you don&apos;t need to format the disk over and over, you just need to copy the image files to the USB drive and boot them directly. You can copy many files at a time and Ventoy will give you a boot menu to select them.
</Description>
